tool_description: This API provides on a monthly basis, the amount of nitrous oxide in the atmosphere from 2001 to the present. Expressed as a mole fraction in dry air, parts per million (ppm).
title: Atmosphere nitrous oxide levels

api_list.name: Nitrous endpoint
api_list.description: The response will be an object with no CORS resources enabled.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://atmosphere-nitrous-oxide-levels.p.rapidapi.com/api/nitrous-oxide-api"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "atmosphere-nitrous-oxide-levels.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
